<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</> values</para>
-->
<para>
为<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</>值修复了<function>EXTRACT(EPOCH)</>
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix mis-display of negative fractional seconds in
<type>INTERVAL</> values</para>
-->
<para>
修复了<type>INTERVAL</>值中负分数秒的错误显示
</para>
<!--
<para>
This error only occurred when the
<literal>&#045;-enable-integer-datetimes</> configuration switch had been used.
</para>
-->
<para>
这个错误只有在使用了<literal>--enable-integer-datetimes</>配置开关的时候发生。
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Additional buffer overrun checks in plpgsql
(Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
在plpgsql中额外的缓冲区溢出检查(Neil)
</para></listitem>
