<para>Restore creation of OID column in CREATE TABLE AS / SELECT INTO</para>
-->
<para>
恢复CREATE TABLE AS / SELECT INTO中OID字段的创建
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix <application>pg_dump</> core dump when dumping views having comments</para>
-->
<para>
当转储的视图有注释时修复<application>pg_dump</>内核转储
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Dump DEFERRABLE/INITIALLY DEFERRED constraints properly</para>
-->
<para>
适当的转储DEFERRABLE/INITIALLY DEFERRED约束
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix UPDATE when child table's column numbering differs from parent</para>
-->
<para>
当子表字段编号与父表不同时辅修UPDATE
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Increase default value of max_fsm_relations</para>
-->
<para>
增加max_fsm_relations的缺省值
</para></listitem>
