<sect1 id="release-7-3">
 <!-- 
 <title>Release 7.3</title>
 -->
 <title>版本 7.3</title>

 <note>
  <!--
  <title>Release Date</title>
  -->
  <title>发布日期</title>
  <simpara>2002-11-27</simpara>
 </note>

 <sect2>
  <!--
  <title>Overview</title>
  -->
  <title>概述</title>

  <!--
<para>
   Major changes in this release:
  </para>
-->
<para>
主要的变化有：
</para>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Schemas</term>
-->
<term>模式</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Schemas allow users to create objects in separate namespaces,
      so two people or applications can have tables with the same
      name. There is also a public schema for shared tables.
      Table/index creation can be restricted by removing privileges
      on the public schema.
     </para>
-->
<para>
模式允许用户在独立的命名空间中创建对象，所以两个人或应用可以有相同名字的表。
还有一个为共享表提供的公共模式。表/索引的创建可以通过在公共模式上删除权限来限制。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Drop Column</term>
-->
<term>删除字段</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> now supports the
      <literal>ALTER TABLE ... DROP COLUMN</literal> functionality.
     </para>
-->
<para>
<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>现在支持<literal>ALTER TABLE ... DROP COLUMN</literal>功能。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!-- 
<term>Table Functions</term>
-->
<term>表函数</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Functions returning multiple rows and/or multiple columns are
      now much easier to use than before.  You can call such a
      <quote>table function</quote> in the <literal>SELECT</literal>
      <literal>FROM</literal> clause, treating its output like a
      table. Also, <application>PL/pgSQL</application> functions can
      now return sets.
     </para>
-->
<para>
返回多个行和/或多个列的函数比以前更好用了。你可以在<literal>SELECT</literal> 
<literal>FROM</literal>子句中调用这样的一个<quote>表函数</quote>，
把它的输出当做一个表。还有<application>PL/pgSQL</application>函数现在可以返回集合了。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Prepared Queries</term>
-->
<term>预备查询</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> now supports prepared
      queries, for improved performance.
     </para>
-->
<para>
<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>现在支持预备查询，以提升性能。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Dependency Tracking</term>
-->
<term>依赖追踪</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> now records object
      dependencies, which allows improvements in many areas.
      <command>DROP</command> statements now take either
      <literal>CASCADE</> or <literal>RESTRICT</> to control whether
      dependent objects are also dropped.
     </para>
-->
<para>
<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>现在记录对象依赖关系，允许了在许多方面的改进。
<command>DROP</command>语句现在接受<literal>CASCADE</> 或 <literal>RESTRICT</>
来控制是否删除依赖对象。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Privileges</term>
-->
<term>权限</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Functions and procedural languages now have privileges, and
      functions can be defined to run with the privileges of their
      creator.
     </para>
-->
<para>
函数和过程语言现在有权限了，并且函数可以定义为用它们的创建者的权限运行。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!-- 
<term>Internationalization</term>
-->
<term>国际化</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Both multibyte and locale support are now always enabled.
     </para>
-->
<para>
现在总是启用多字节和本地支持。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Logging</term>
-->
<term>日志</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      A variety of logging options have been enhanced.
     </para>
-->
<para>
各种日志选项都增强了。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Interfaces</term>
-->
<term>接口</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      A large number of interfaces have been moved to <ulink
      url="http://gborg.postgresql.org">http://gborg.postgresql.org</>
      where they can be developed and released independently.
     </para>
-->
<para>
大量的接口已经移动到了<ulink url="http://gborg.postgresql.org">http://gborg.postgresql.org</>，
在这里它们可以独立的开发和发布。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <!--
<term>Functions/Identifiers</term>
-->
<term>函数/标识符</term>
    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      By default, functions can now take up to 32 parameters, and
      identifiers can be up to 63 bytes long.  Also, <literal>OPAQUE</>
      is now deprecated: there are specific <quote>pseudo-datatypes</>
      to represent each of the former meanings of <literal>OPAQUE</>
      in function argument and result types.
     </para>
-->
<para>
缺省的，函数现在可以接受多达32个参数，标识符可以多达63个字节长度。
还有，<literal>OPAQUE</>现在已经废弃了：特定的<quote>pseudo-datatypes</>
在函数参数和结果类型中表示<literal>OPAQUE</>之前的含义。
</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

  </variablelist>
 </sect2>

 <sect2>
  <!--
  <title>Migration to Version 7.3</title>
  -->
  <title>迁移到版本 7.3</title>

  <!--
<para>
   A dump/restore using <application>pg_dump</> is required for those
   wishing to migrate data from any previous release. If your
   application examines the system catalogs, additional changes will
   be required due to the introduction of schemas in 7.3; for more
   information, see: <ulink
   url="http://developer.postgresql.org/~momjian/upgrade_tips_7.3"></>.
  </para>
-->
<para>
那些想要从任何先前的版本中迁移数据的需要使用<application>pg_dump</>的转储/恢复。
如果你的应用检索系统表，那么需要做额外的改变，由于7.3中模式的引入；要获取更多信息，
请参阅<ulink url="http://developer.postgresql.org/~momjian/upgrade_tips_7.3"></>。
</para>

  <!--
<para>
   Observe the following incompatibilities:
  </para>
-->
<para>
观察下列的不一致性：
</para>

  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     Pre-6.3 clients are no longer supported.
    </para>
-->
<para>
不再支持6.3之前的客户端。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> now has a column for the user
     name and additional features.  Existing files need to be
     adjusted.
    </para>
-->
<para>
<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>现在有一个用户名和额外特征的字段。
现存的文件需要调整。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     Several <filename>postgresql.conf</filename> logging parameters
     have been renamed.
    </para>
-->
<para>
几个<filename>postgresql.conf</filename>日志参数已经重命名了。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     <literal>LIMIT #,#</literal> has been disabled; use
     <literal>LIMIT # OFFSET #</literal>.
    </para>
-->
<para>
<literal>LIMIT #,#</literal>已经禁用了，请使用<literal>LIMIT # OFFSET #</literal>。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     <command>INSERT</command> statements with column lists must
     specify a value for each specified column. For example,
     <literal>INSERT INTO tab (col1, col2) VALUES ('val1')</literal>
     is now invalid.  It's still allowed to supply fewer columns than
     expected if the <command>INSERT</command> does not have a column list.
    </para>
-->
<para>
带有字段列表的<command>INSERT</command>语句必须为每个声明的字段声明值。例如，
<literal>INSERT INTO tab (col1, col2) VALUES ('val1')</literal>现在是非法的。
如果<command>INSERT</command>没有字段列表，那么仍然允许提供少于期望的字段。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     <type>serial</type> columns are no longer automatically
     <literal>UNIQUE</>; thus, an index will not automatically be
     created.
    </para>
-->
<para>
<type>serial</type>字段不再自动<literal>UNIQUE</>；因此，不会自动创建一个索引。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     A <command>SET</command> command inside an aborted transaction
     is now rolled back.
    </para>
-->
<para>
现在在退出的事务内部的<command>SET</command>命令会回滚。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     <command>COPY</command> no longer considers missing trailing
     columns to be null.  All columns need to be specified.
     (However, one can achieve a similar effect by specifying a
     column list in the <command>COPY</command> command.)
    </para>
-->
<para>
<command>COPY</command>不再认为丢失的后续字段为空。需要指定所有的字段。
（不过，可以通过在<command>COPY</command>命令中声明一个字段列表达到相似的效果。）
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     The data type <type>timestamp</type> is now equivalent to
     <type>timestamp without time zone</type>, instead of
     <type>timestamp with time zone</type>.
    </para>
-->
<para>
数据类型<type>timestamp</type>现在相当于<type>timestamp without time zone</type>，
而不是<type>timestamp with time zone</type>。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     Pre-7.3 databases loaded into 7.3 will not have the new object
     dependencies for <type>serial</type> columns, unique
     constraints, and foreign keys. See the directory
     <filename>contrib/adddepend/</filename> for a detailed
     description and a script that will add such dependencies.
    </para>
-->
<para>
7.3之前的数据库加载到7.3将没有<type>serial</type>字段、唯一约束和外键的新对象依赖性。
参阅目录<filename>contrib/adddepend/</filename>获取一个详细的描述和一个添加这样的依赖性的脚本。
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
<para>
     An empty string (<literal>''</literal>) is no longer allowed as
     the input into an integer field.  Formerly, it was silently
     interpreted as 0.
    </para>
-->
<para>
不再允许空字符串(<literal>''</literal>)作为整数字段的输入。原先，它被隐式的解释为0。
</para>
   </listitem>

  </itemizedlist>
 </sect2>

 <sect2>
  <!-- 
  <title>Changes</title>
  -->
  <title>修改列表</title>

  <sect3>
   <!--
   <title>Server Operation</title>
   -->
   <title>服务器操作</title>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><!--
<para>Add pg_locks view to show locks (Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
添加pg_locks视图以显示锁(Neil)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Security fixes for password negotiation memory allocation (Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
为密码协商内存分配修复安全性(Neil)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Remove support for version 0 FE/BE protocol (<productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 6.2 and earlier) (Tom)</para>
-->
<para>
删除对版本 0 FE/BE 协议的支持（<productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 6.2和之前的版本）(Tom)
