 <sect1 id="release-7-2-8">
  <!--
  <title>Release 7.2.8</title>
  -->
  <title>版本 7.2.8</title>

  <note>
  <!--
  <title>Release Date</title>
  -->
  <title>发布日期</title>
  <simpara>2005-05-09</simpara>
  </note>

  <!--
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 7.2.7, including one
   security-related issue.
  </para>
-->
<para>
这个版本包含自7.2.7以来的各种补丁，包括一个安全相关的问题。
</para>

  <sect2>
   <!--
   <title>Migration to Version 7.2.8</title>
   -->
   <title>迁移到版本 7.2.8</title>

   <!--
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 7.2.X.
   </para>
-->
<para>
运行7.2.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。
</para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
   <!-- 
   <title>Changes</title>
   -->
   <title>修改列表</title>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><!--
<para>Repair ancient race condition that allowed a transaction to be
seen as committed for some purposes (eg SELECT FOR UPDATE) slightly sooner
than for other purposes</para>
-->
<para>
修复过时的竞态条件，该条件允许一个事务因为某些目的被视作已提交(如SELECT FOR UPDATE)
</para>
<!--
<para>This is an extremely serious bug since it could lead to apparent
data inconsistencies being briefly visible to applications.</para>
-->
<para>
这是一个非常严重的bug，因为它会导致表面上数据的不一致被应用短暂的看到。
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Repair race condition between relation extension and
VACUUM</para>
-->
<para>
修复关系扩展和VACUUM之间的竞态条件。
</para>
<!--
<para>This could theoretically have caused loss of a page's worth of
freshly-inserted data, although the scenario seems of very low probability.
There are no known cases of it having caused more than an Assert failure.
</para>
-->
<para>
理论上这可能导致丢失新插入的一页数据，尽管该情况看起来概率很低。
没有导致多于一个维护失败的已知情况。
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix <function>EXTRACT(EPOCH)</> for
<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</> values</para>
-->
<para>
为<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</>值修复<function>EXTRACT(EPOCH)</>
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Additional buffer overrun checks in plpgsql
(Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
在plpgsql中额外的缓存溢出检查(Neil)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix pg_dump to dump index names and trigger names containing
<literal>%</> correctly (Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
修复pg_dump以正确的转储包含<literal>%</>的索引名和触发器名
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Prevent <function>to_char(interval)</> from dumping core for
month-related formats</para>
-->
<para>
阻止<function>to_char(interval)</>转储月份相关格式的内核
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix <filename>contrib/pgcrypto</> for newer OpenSSL builds
(Marko Kreen)</para>
-->
<para>
为更新的OpenSSL构建修复<filename>contrib/pgcrypto</> (Marko Kreen)
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

 </sect2>
</sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-7-2-7">
  <!--
  <title>Release 7.2.7</title>
  -->
  <title>版本 7.2.7</title>

  <note>
  <!--
  <title>Release Date</title>
  -->
  <title>发布日期</title>
  <simpara>2005-01-31</simpara>
  </note>

  <!--
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 7.2.6, including several
   security-related issues.
  </para>
-->
<para>
这个版本包含自7.2.6以来的各种补丁，包括几个安全相关的问题。
</para>

  <sect2>
   <!--
   <title>Migration to Version 7.2.7</title>
   -->
   <title>迁移到版本 7.2.7</title>

   <!--
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 7.2.X.
   </para>
-->
<para>
运行7.2.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。
</para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
   <!-- 
   <title>Changes</title>
   -->
   <title>修改列表</title>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><!--
<para>Disallow <command>LOAD</> to non-superusers</para>
-->
<para>
不允许非超级用户<command>LOAD</>
</para>
<!--
<para>
On platforms that will automatically execute initialization functions of a
shared library (this includes at least Windows and ELF-based Unixen),
<command>LOAD</> can be used to make the server execute arbitrary code.
Thanks to NGS Software for reporting this.</para>
-->
<para>
在平台上会自动执行共享库的初始化函数（至少包括Windows和ELF-based Unixen），
<command>LOAD</>可以用来使服务器执行任意的代码。感谢NGS Software报告这个问题。
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Add needed STRICT marking to some contrib functions (Kris
Jurka)</para>
-->
<para>
添加需要的STRICT标记到一些贡献包功能(Kris Jurka)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Avoid buffer overrun when plpgsql cursor declaration has too
many parameters (Neil)</para>
-->
<para>
当plpgsql的游标声明有太多的参数时避免缓冲区溢出(Neil)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix planning error for FULL and RIGHT outer joins</para>
-->
<para>
修复全外连接和右外连接的规划错误
</para>
<!--
<para>
The result of the join was mistakenly supposed to be sorted the same as the
left input.  This could not only deliver mis-sorted output to the user, but
in case of nested merge joins could give outright wrong answers.
</para>
-->
<para>
连接的结果错误的与左输入有相同的排序。这不只是发送错误排序的输出给用户，
还在嵌套的合并连接的情况下给出完全错误的回复。
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix display of negative intervals in SQL and GERMAN
datestyles</para>
-->
<para>
修复SQL和GERMAN数据类型中负数间隔的显示
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

 </sect2>
</sect1>

