  <simpara>2004-08-16</simpara>
  </note>

  <!--
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 7.2.4.
  </para>
-->
<para>
这个版本包含自7.2.4以来的各种修复。
</para>


  <sect2>
   <!--
   <title>Migration to Version 7.2.5</title>
   -->
