修复<function>to_ascii</function>里的缓冲区溢出(Guido Notari)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix core dump in deadlock detection on machines where char is unsigned</para>
-->
<para>
修复机器上无符号字符的死锁检测里的内核转储
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Fix failure to respond to <command>pg_ctl stop -m fast</command> after Async_NotifyHandler runs</para>
-->
<para>
修复运行Async_NotifyHandler之后未能响应<command>pg_ctl stop -m fast</command>
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Repair memory leaks in pg_dump</para>
-->
<para>
修复pg_dump中的内存泄露
</para></listitem>
<listitem><!--
<para>Avoid conflict with system definition of <function>isblank()</function> function or macro</para>
-->
<para>
避免与<function>isblank()</function>函数或宏的系统定义冲突
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
 </sect2>
</sect1>

